{"tid":1125641,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"傳黃心穎求馬國明復合 對唔住明哥哥! 果晚「飲大咗」","createTime":"2019-04-25T23:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T03:46:06.000Z","uid":72009,"like":26,"dislike":412,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"401a6e423edd288d2a0fdc7efdb24c2c4aa1e067","tid":1125641,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T23:57:22.000Z","msg":"眼見事業一鋪清袋，昨日有報道又指心穎為挽救事業，居然仍不斷找馬國明（馬明）求復合博翻身，仲向對方自稱「飲大咗」，兼且不捨得這段感情，雖然馬明一度心軟，但身邊朋友都不支持復合，就連黃爸爸都對囡囡一事「冇眼睇」。 <br />\n此外，有份出席「安心偷食」飯局的馬志威，昨日出席活動時直言跟安仔較熟，但不清楚「安心」關係，事後亦有傳短訊慰問對方，他說：「不過佢冇覆，都擔心佢情緒，想盡快平息呢件事。（你有冇搵心穎？）都有，但冇覆。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/entertainment/news/「安心」合體節目遭腰斬-傳黃心穎求馬國明復合/ar-BBWi7ye?ocid=spartandhp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fentertainment%2Fnews%2F%E3%80%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E3%80%8D%E5%90%88%E9%AB%94%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E9%81%AD%E8%85%B0%E6%96%AC-%E5%82%B3%E9%BB%83%E5%BF%83%E7%A9%8E%E6%B1%82%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%8E%E5%BE%A9%E5%90%88%2Far-BBWi7ye%3Focid%3Dspartandhp&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreGa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=adcbdd2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/entertainment/news/「安心」合體節目遭腰斬-傳黃心穎求馬國明復合/ar-BBWi7ye?ocid=spartandhp</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />馬明唔忍係呀"},{"pid":"6fbe9af3f5cb66372d94ea156467b00084c3ba2c","tid":1125641,"uid":165510,"like":850,"dislike":2,"score":848,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T23:59:33.000Z","msg":"如果咁都忍得真係屎都食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n馬明無女都咪揀返佢"},{"pid":"1fe97c16d516f9772e8b574509185ee1b1a4c9ae","tid":1125641,"uid":73092,"like":202,"dislike":2,"score":200,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T00:02:54.000Z","msg":"返加拿大算喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d03b17fd801a6f8c3d990f690efaee78dbaffec","tid":1125641,"uid":249933,"like":87,"dislike":2,"score":85,"cit